agel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20photo%20tells%20a%20thousand%20words%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-profile-pictures-no-selfies-pets-write-good-bio-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehaving%20more%20than%20two%20photos%20%3C%2Fa%3Eups%20your%20chances%20of%20getting%20a%20solid%20match%2C%20the%20CEOs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuay%20said%20that%20photos%20give%20people%20important%20information%20that%20helps%20them%20make%20a%20smart%20decision%20about%20whether%20to%20swipe%20right%2C%20so%20CMB%20users%20have%20to%20upload%20at%20least%20two%20pictures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20order%20of%20business%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20pictures%20are%20of%20yourself%2C%20or%20risk%20getting%20barred%20from%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsers%20who%20put%20out%20images%20that%20are%20not%20human%20%E2%80%94%20that%20means%20it%20could%20be%20anime%20photos%2C%20part%20of%20a%20scenery%2C%20or%20a%20backdrop%20%E2%80%94%20they%20get%20hidden%20and%20banned%2C%26quot%3B%20Juay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20the%20two%20pictures%2C%20Juay%20and%20Yang%20have%20strict%20dos%20and%20don'ts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuay%20said%20ensuring%20that%20your%20photos%20don't%20show%20a%20side%20view%20of%20your%20face%2C%20or%20obscure%20your%20face%2C%20is%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftinder-bumble-scientist-smile-online-dating-photo-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elowest%20hanging%20fruit%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20of%20course%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20stand%20out%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20just%20a%20passport%20photo%20of%20yourself%2C%20where%20you%20don't%20look%20attractive%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20like%20to%20cook%2C%20if%20you%20like%20to%20do%20gardening%2C%20you%20like%20to%20do%20rock%20climbing%20or%20kayaking%2C%20show%20yourself%20in%20the%20photo%20doing%20the%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuay%20added%20that%20users%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrop-your-friends-out-photos-better-dating-profile-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshould%20not%20have%20other%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20photos%20they%20have%20on%20their%20dating%20app%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYang%20recommended%20keeping%20the%20photos%20more%20conservative%20for%20serious%20dating%20apps%20like%20CMB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20those%20selfies%20that%20I%20see%20on%20the%20other%20apps%2C%20where%20they're%20taking%20a%20picture%20in%20the%20mirror%2C%20almost%20half%20naked%2C%20that's%20probably%20not%20appropriate%20for%20the%20community%20that%20we%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20And%20add%20at%20least%20one%20prompt%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Including%20prompts%20in%20dating%20profiles%20increases%20the%20chances%20of%20finding%20a%20match%2C%20per%20Coffee%20Meets%20Bagel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fad912599d46a4ccc0c3b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIncluding%20prompts%20in%20dating%20profiles%20increases%20the%20chances%20of%20finding%20a%20match%2C%20per%20Coffee%20Meets%20Bagel.%3Cp%3EScreengrabs%2FCoffee%20Meets%20Bagel%20app%2C%20Coffee%20Meets%20Bagel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESupplementing%20photos%20with%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhinge-ceo-justin-mcleod-dating-app-evaluates-overused-prompts-2021-04%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efun%20facts%20about%20yourself%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20also%20important%2C%20the%20execs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20go%20from%20just%20zero%20to%20one%20prompt%2C%20there's%20a%20very%20big%20difference%20in%20connection%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20Yang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaters%20with%20longer%20prompt%20answers%C2%A0that%20contain%20more%20than%20one%20sentence%20get%2054%25%20more%20likes%2C%20and%20daters%20with%20at%20least%20one%20prompt%20filled%20out%20are%20twice%20as%20likely%20to%20find%20a%20match%2C%20CMB's%20press%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20fill%20out%20your%20profile%2C%20the%20more%20people%20who%20read%20your%20profile%20can%20understand%20about%20your%20personal%20interests%2C%20your%20traits%2C%20and%20your%20aspirations.%20It's%20more%20telling%20about%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Juay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20is%20for%20the%20prompts%20to%20be%20substantial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20say%2C%20'I%20am%20a%20Virgo%2C'%20and%20you%20stop%20at%20that%2C%20it%20doesn't%20say%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Juay%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20actually%20extend%20it%20out%20a%20little%20bit%20with%20at%20least%20one%20more%20sentence%2C%20like%20'I'm%20a%20Virgo%20who%20likes%20to%20do%20something.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Choose%20deal%20breakers%20very%20carefully%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20list%20of%20filters%20that%20Coffee%20Meets%20Bagel%20offers%20its%20users.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68fad8b4c007ca8c27378c08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20CEOs%20encouraged%20users%20to%20choose%20dealbreakers%20carefully.%3Cp%3EScreengrabs%2FCoffee%20Meets%20Bagel%20app%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executives'%20last%20bit%20of%20advice%20for%20dating%20app%20profiles%20was%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-not-list-ultimatums-dealbreakers-non-negotiables-in-dating-profiles-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejudicious%20with%20dealbreakers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20allows%20users%20to%20set%20several%20dealbreakers%2C%20such%20as%20gender%2C%20age%20range%2C%20height%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20religion%2C%20relationship%20goals%2C%20and%20proximity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExamples%20of%20dealbreakers%20would%20be%2C%20say%2C%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20Juay%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20Christian%2C%20and%20you%20only%20want%20to%20date%20a%20fellow%20Christian%2C%20that%20is%20fair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOr%20relationship%20goals%2C%20some%20people%20especially%20filter%20out%20for%20marriage%20because%20they%20have%20marriage%20in%20mind.%20Or%20people%20are%20very%20clear%20about%20family%20goals%2C%20like%20whether%20they%20want%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20filters%2C%20like%20height%20or%20education%2C%20should%20be%20applied%20thoughtfully%2C%20Juay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20so%20many%20happy%20couples%20where%20there's%20a%20mismatch%20in%20height%20expectations%2C%20but%20they%20have%20been%20happily%20married%20because%20height%20really%20doesn't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEducation%20or%20job%20titles%2C%20too%2C%20should%20not%20make%20or%20break%20the%20match.%20The%20bulk%20of%20CMB's%20users%2C%20she%20said%2C%20are%20between%2025%20and%2032%20years%20old%2C%20a%20stage%20in%20life%20when%20education%20and%20jobs%20are%20transient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20always%20go%20for%20a%20higher%20degree%20or%20you%20get%20promoted%20along%20the%20way%2C%20but%20not%20at%20age%2028%20years%20old%2C%20where%20everybody's%20probably%20still%20really%20early%20in%20their%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20of%20users%20who%20are%20very%20strict%3B%20they%20have%20a%20really%2C%20really%20long%20list%20of%20filters%2C%20which%20is%20not%20helping%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoffee-meets-bagel-serious-match-non-negotiables-dating-