he%20complications%20of%20a%20blended%20family%2C%20it's%20even%20more%20important%20to%20center%20conversations%20about%20love%20and%20money%20around%20the%20legacy%20that%20you%20wish%20to%20leave%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glenmede.com%2Fprivate-wealth-management%2Fpalm-beach%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParthemer%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20refers%20to%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Bbeginning%20with%20the%20end%20in%20mind.%26quot%3B%20Consider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealth-advisor-financial-therapist-how-to-talk-about-inheritance-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20purpose%20you've%20chosen%20for%20your%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%2C%20reverse%20engineer%20an%20estate%20plan%20that%20delivers%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20you%20might%20be%20happy%20for%20your%20widow(er)%20to%20remarry%20in%20the%20event%20of%20your%20death%2C%20but%20wouldn't%20want%20their%20new%20spouse%20to%20have%20access%20to%20funds%20that%20might%20otherwise%20go%20to%20your%20children%20and%20grandchildren.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20you%20could%20leave%20a%20set%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20your%20widow(er)%2C%20and%20also%20give%20inheritance%20to%20your%20children%20or%20grandchildren%20directly%2C%20or%20protect%20it%20in%20a%20trust%20for%20them%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0ba976c-e8b5-40d1-a5b8-668de1d14943%5C%22%3EIdeally%2C%20start%20with%20a%20prenup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20prenuptial%20agreement%20%E2%80%94%20which%20outlines%20which%20assets%20in%20a%20marriage%20are%20shared%2C%20and%20which%20remain%20separate%20property%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20being%20prepared%20for%20estate%20planning%20in%20a%20world%20where%20divorce%20is%20common%2C%20Parthemer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-are-not-rich-but-we-are-still-signing-prenup-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Especifics%20of%20a%20prenup%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20highly%20individual%2C%20but%20they%20can%20stipulate%20that%20inheritance%20not%20be%20considered%20a%20shared%20asset%20if%20a%20divorce%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20prenup%2C%20it's%20easy%20for%20inheritance%20to%20become%20shared%20property%20with%20your%20spouse%2C%20which%20means%20that%20they're%20entitled%20to%20a%20portion%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECates%20worked%20with%20a%20family%20where%20the%20matriarch%20left%20a%20beach%20house%20to%20her%20daughter.%20The%20daughter%20and%20her%20husband%20at%20the%20time%20used%20the%20house%20personally%20and%20rented%20it%20out.%20When%20they%20divorced%2C%20the%20husband%20was%20entitled%20to%20partial%20ownership%20of%20the%20home%2C%20even%20though%20Cates%20says%20it%20was%20clear%20the%20mother%20intended%20the%20home%20to%20belong%20to%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheharrispoll.com%2Fbriefs%2Fpopularity-of-prenups-rising-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15%25%20of%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20have%20been%20married%20have%20signed%20a%20prenup%2C%20according%20to%20a%202022%20poll%2C%20but%20data%20show%20the%20agreements%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%2C%20and%2042%25%20of%20Americans%20say%20they%20support%20the%20use%20of%20prenups.%20Experts%20say%20that's%20because%20people%20have%20seen%20firsthand%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-early-20-years-ago-saving-planning-advice-social-security-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eharm%20divorces%20can%20have%20on%20finances%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20them%20have%20realized%20that%20a%20divorce%20or%20separation%20can%20unravel%20generations%20of%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisfirst.com%2Fabout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELibby%20Leffler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20First%2C%20an%20online%20prenup%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Libby%20Leffler%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6908cf32599d46a4ccc1550b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221708%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrenups%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%2C%20Libby%20Leffler%20said.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Libby%20Leffler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELeffler%20regularly%20sees%20the%20older%20generation%20reaching%20out%20to%20First%20to%20get%20information%20on%20how%20their%20adult%20children%20can%20set%20up%20prenups.%20She%20also%20sees%20the%20younger%20generation%20encouraging%20their%20parents%20to%20sign%20a%20prenup%20before%20remarrying%20in%20their%20golden%20years.%20So%2C%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20talk%20with%20your%20loved%20ones%20about%20the%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20say%20there's%20some%20taboo%20about%20prenups%20among%20the%20older%20generations%2C%20but%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Z%20have%20few%20hangups%20about%20the%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20the%20conversation%20around%20prenups%20as%20being%20totally%20mainstream%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20as%20if%20we're%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20generational%20shift%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20people%20are%20talking%20about%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22764d12e4-5f10-4861-bd52-578e2a95e563%5C%22%3EPause%20before%20using%20inheritance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20prenup%20in%20place%2C%20but%20receive%20an%20inheritance%2C%20Cates%20recommends%20pausing%20to%20talk%20to%20an%20attorney%20and%20a%20wealth%20advisor%20before%20using%20any%20of%20the%20money%20or%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20you'll%20put%20a%20postnup%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20referring%20to%20an%20agreement%20that%2C%20like%20a%20prenup%2C%20outlines%20how%20assets%20are%20to%20be%20handled%20in%20the%20event%20of%20divorce%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20inheritance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffight-over-who-inherits-wealth-how-to-decide-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einheritance%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20automatically%20considered%20marital%20property%2C%20Cates%20explains.%20However%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20funds%20are%20mingled%20with%20marital%20assets%20or%20used%20to%20support%20the%20family%2C%20your%20spouse%20may%20have%20a%20claim%20to%20them%20%E2%80%94%20like%20that%20beach%20house%20she%20mentioned%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263b2db8b-55d8-4a7a-90ec-7f44bab9b450%5C%22%3EConsider%20a%20stealth%20prenup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20older%20generation%20ultimately%20can't%20control%20whether%20their%20children%20and%20grandchildren%20get%20prenups.%20However%2C%20they%20can%20structure%20their%20estate%20plan%20%26quot%3Bto%20minimize%20the%20need%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20to%20have%20a%20prenup%2C%26quot%3B%20Parthemer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20calls%20this%20the%20stealth%20prenup%2C%20but%20emphasizes%20that%20there's%20nothing%20sneaky%20about%20it.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20stealth%20prenup%20can%20be%20a%20gift%20to%20future%20generations%20because%20it%20%26quot%3Bcan%20ease%20the%20whole%20prenup%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20a%20stealth%20prenup%20is%20something%20to%20talk%20with%20your%20lawyer%20about%2C%20but%20here's%20an%20overview%20of%20how%20it%20works%3A%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20these%20agreements%20is%20an%20irrevocable%2C%20fully%20discretionary%20trust%2C%20Parthemer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20there%20are%20no%20automatic%20payments%20from%20the%20trust%20%E2%80%94%20how%20and%20when%20assets%20are%20distributed%20are%20entirely%20at%20the%20discretion%20of%20the%20trustee%20(a%20person%2C%20who%20can%20be%20a%20relative%20or%20a%20professional%2C%20who%20has%20been%20appointed%20to%20manage%20the%20trust).%20Since%20the%20beneficiary%20doesn't%20have%20any%20entitlement%20to%20the%20funds%20in%20the%20trust%2C%20their%20creditors%20and%2For%20spouse%20have%20no%20entitlement%20to%20the%20funds%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20creates%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20protection%20from%20an%20ex-spouse%20trying%20to%20reach%20through%20and%20grab%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20Parthemer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-protect-estate-inheritance-prenup-postnup-stealth-prenup-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762200661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6903891ac007ca8c2737ee5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-protect-estate-inheritance-prenup-postnup-stealth-prenup-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20financial%20experts%20explain%20prenups%2C%20postnups%2C%20stealth%20prenups%2C%20and%20why%20you%20should%20talk%20to%20an%20attorney%20before%20using%20inheritance%20for%20your%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-protect-estate-inheritance-prenup-postnup-stealth-prenup-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20backs%20Cuomo%20against%20Zohran%20Mamdani%20in%20NYC%20mayoral%20race%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zohran%20Mamdani%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20and%20Andrew%20Cuomo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69090e4d599d46a4ccc1